        {
            "title": "保誠擬委任滙控前主席范智廉為非執董兼候任主席",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">保誠(02378)宣布，將委任范智廉(Sir Douglas Flint)為非執行董事及候任主席，並缃於5月底股東週年大會後接替Shriti Vadera擔任董事會主席。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"保誠官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/02378-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"保誠官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/02378-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">保誠官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">范智廉是滙控(00005)前主席，曾在滙豐任職逾20年，於1995年至2010年擔任集團財務董事，其後於2010年至2017年擔任集團主席。自2018年起，他一直擔任 Aberdeen Group plc 及 IP Group plc的主席。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">保誠預期，范智廉爵士將於3月加入董事會(待監管批准)，以便在Shriti離職前能有序地進行交接<br/>  工作。他亦將加入提名與管治委員會及薪酬委員會。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">Shriti將於5月底股東週年大會後退任董事會，届時她將已完成6年的任期。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15581192-%e4%bf%9d%e8%aa%a0%e6%93%ac%e5%a7%94%e4%bb%bb%e6%bb%99%e6%8e%a7%e5%89%8d%e4%b8%bb%e5%b8%ad%e8%8c%83%e6%99%ba%e5%bb%89%e7%82%ba%e9%9d%9e%e5%9f%b7%e8%91%a3%e5%85%bc%e5%80%99%e4%bb%bb%e4%b8%bb%e5%b8%ad",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/02378.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 12:50:40",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "周大福創建申請註冊總額不逾50億元人幣熊貓債券計畫",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">周大福創建(00659)公布，已向中國銀行間市場交易商協會申請，註冊總金額不高於50億元(人民幣‧下同)的熊貓債券計畫。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"周大福創建官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/00659.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"周大福創建官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/00659.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">周大福創建官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司於2023年已申請註冊熊貓債券計畫，這批2023年熊貓債券計畫最後共發行3批、總額36億元的3年期債券，將於今年5月底至明年3月到期。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">周大福創建在公告中表示，由於2023年熊貓債券計畫已於2025年4月屆滿，公司因此向協會申請註冊2026年熊貓債券計畫，預期在兩年內發行。申請正在處理中，申請能否及何時獲批等尚未確定。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司進一步指出，在預期美元/港元借貸與人民幣借貸之間的有利利率差將持續存在，2026年熊貓債券計劃可為公司提供一個具成本效益的方式，為(其中包括)將於2026年及2027年到期償還的票據的未償還本金額作出再融資。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">此外，由於周大福創建的資產、營運及收入當中相當部分以人民幣計值，2026年熊貓債券將可繼續作為對人民幣匯率波動的自然對沖。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15581158-%e5%91%a8%e5%a4%a7%e7%a6%8f%e5%89%b5%e5%bb%ba%e7%94%b3%e8%ab%8b%e8%a8%bb%e5%86%8a%e7%b8%bd%e9%a1%8d%e4%b8%8d%e9%80%be50%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3%e7%86%8a%e8%b2%93%e5%82%b5%e5%88%b8%e8%a8%88",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/00659-2024.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 12:35:36",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "銀價升至90美元　創新高　金價在高位徘徊",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金價及銀價持續向好，受到減息預期、地緣政治局勢緊張、需求強勁等帶動。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">現貨銀首次升至每盎司90美元，上升3%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">現貨金徘徊於高位，較早時報每盎司4629美元，上升近1%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15581137-%e9%8a%80%e5%83%b9%e5%8d%87%e8%87%b390%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e3%80%80%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98%e3%80%80%e9%87%91%e5%83%b9%e5%9c%a8%e9%ab%98%e4%bd%8d%e5%be%98%e5%be%8a-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251014_FI_source_licensed_shutterstock_2009158820.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 12:20:31",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "半日收市︱越兩萬七 恒指升244點報27092點 阿里系再成火車頭",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地最新進出口數據勝預期支撐滬深A股揚升，港股今早亦隨之重拾動力，重新收復兩萬七關口，阿里系繼續擔當升市火車頭。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240909_FI_source-ap_China_Trade_704.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240909_FI_source-ap_China_Trade_704.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數高開123點後，初段升幅曾收窄僅4點，低見26852點，在內地公布進出口數字再加上滬深A股明顯升溫，港股回復向上走勢，早市中段終於收復兩萬七，後段最高曾見27097點，將升幅擴大至249點，其後略作整固。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240909_FI_source-ap_China_Trade_704.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240909_FI_source-ap_China_Trade_704.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">巴士的報記者攝</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/09988.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\"></h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"快手\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_01024-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"快手\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_01024-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">快手</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：海底撈官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20240617_FI_source-web_06862_1200.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：海底撈官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20240617_FI_source-web_06862_1200.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：海底撈官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240909_FI_source-ap_China_Trade_704.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">巴士的報記者攝</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\"></h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"快手\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_01024-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">快手</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：海底撈官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/644x392/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20240617_FI_source-web_06862_1200.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：海底撈官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指中午收報27092點，仍漲244點或0.91%。恒生科技指數重新領跑，半日揚升89點或1.53%，報5959點；國企指數升81點或0.88%，報9367點。主板半日成交1626.74億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日升267點，報27130點，高水37點。科指期貨升88點，報5973點，高水13點。國指期貨升89點，報9384點，高水17點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里系繼續吸引投資者的眼球，阿里巴巴(09988)剛預告，將於明早上午10時直播千問APP發布會，見證AI如何開啟辦事時代。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該股的ADR昨晚已偷步造好，阿里巴巴股份今早在港亦高開2.44%，早市全程報升，低位162.1元時仍漲1.38%，最高曾見168.4元，升5.23%；中午收報168.3元，漲8.4元或5.25%，單一股份已為恒指提供逾111點進賬，並以211.06億元交投穩佔主板股份成交額首席。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">同系阿里健康(00241)則以升幅登上藍籌最強，半日飆15.9%，報7.58元，創52周新高，成交達31.17億元。上述阿里孖寶均躋身主板股份成交額、以及藍籌升幅10大榜上。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其他重磅科股則互有升跌，快手(01024)官宣擬發行美元及人民幣優先票據，股價今早彈升5.48%，報82.75元；百度(09888)也升2.04%，報145.3元；騰訊(00700)也升1.67%，報638元；小米(01810)反彈0.53%，報38.18元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美團(03690)與京東(09618)則回吐，美團今早平開後迅速轉跌，中午收報101.8元，跌2.96%。京東更在低開後幾乎全程「潛水」，半日跌0.26%，報117.1元；同系京東健康(06618)則跟隨醫療平台股造好，升2.67%，報69.2元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"快手\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_01024-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"快手\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240509_FI_source-web_01024-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">快手</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">部份內地消費概念跑出，海底撈(06862)創始人兼董事長張勇重新擔任CEO，刺激該股今早裂口抽升，最高衝上15.94元，漲10.54%；中午收報15.49元，仍升7.42%，創6個月新高，成交達12.26億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">農夫山泉(09633)獲里昂唱好，上調目標價至57.6元；該股亦乘機湧上，中午收報50.75元，升6.13%，成交也有3.68億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：海底撈官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20240617_FI_source-web_06862_1200.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：海底撈官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20240617_FI_source-web_06862_1200.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：海底撈官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">憧憬澳門今年開局賭收持續強勁，濠賭股跑贏大市。銀河娛樂(00027)升3.86%，報40.32元；金沙中國(01928)升2.59%，報19.01元。美高梅中國(02282)升3.14%，報12.83元；永利澳門(01128)升2.76%，報5.95元；澳博(00880)升1.3%，報2.34元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">異動股方面，丘鈦科技(01478)發盈喜，料去年盈利升4倍至4.5倍；該股今早應聲炒上，飆13.5%，報10.17元。同類股份亦造好，舜宇光學(02382)升1.54%，報66.05元；瑞聲科技(02018)升2.05%，報39.9元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">AI概念股獅騰控股(02562)再現炒作，抽升47.86%，報3.8元，半日成交達14.32億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15581134-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e8%b6%8a%e5%85%a9%e8%90%ac%e4%b8%83-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87244%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b127092%e9%bb%9e-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e7%b3%bb%e5%86%8d%e6%88%90%e7%81%ab",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-8.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 12:20:33",
