        {
            "title": "滬深A股早市顯著回升 受惠最新進出口數字勝預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地今早公布的最新進出口數字勝預期，帶動滬深A股顯著回升，兩市股指齊漲逾1%，滬市再次創逾10年高位。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097543963940-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097543963940-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早低開不足1點後迅速轉升，於上午10時前升幅已擴大至逾20點，隨著內地公布上月進出口數字，大市動力進一步提升，指數亦穩步向上，最高衝上4190點，升52點；滬指中午收報4188點，仍漲49點或1.2%，半日成交8916.71億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指於早市更全程報升，高開24點、報14194點即成半日低位，開市僅約20分鐘升幅已擴大至逾1%，尾段尚不斷試頂，一度高見14459點，升289點；深指中午收報14449點，漲280點或1.98%，成交1.33萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數也升51點或1.08%，收報4812點；創業板指數飆74點或2.24%，報3396點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250409_FI_source-ap_China-2-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250409_FI_source-ap_China-2-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">主要板塊幾乎全部揚升，電子信息類別資金流入最為明顯，國產軟件股岩山科技(002195.SZ)漲9.84%，海格通信(002465.SZ)、烽火通信(600498.SH)等均漲停板。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">芯片及半導體相關股持續強勢，寒武紀(688256.SH)升1.56%，報1430元。峰岹科技(01304)A股(688279.SH)升6.98%，報205.42元；華虹(01347)A股(688347.SH)漲4.07%，報125.88元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15580980-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1a%e8%82%a1%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e9%a1%af%e8%91%97%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%87-%e5%8f%97%e6%83%a0%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e9%80%b2%e5%87%ba%e5%8f%a3%e6%95%b8%e5%ad%97%e5%8b%9d%e9%a0%90%e6%9c%9f",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-12.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 11:40:28",
