            "title": "港股收復兩萬七 阿里孖寶再領漲",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地最近進出口數字勝預期，滬深A股動力明顯提升，港股亦於早市中段重越兩萬七關口。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/Trump_Tariffs_24331540781070.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/Trump_Tariffs_24331540781070.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至上午約10時59分，恒生指數報27041點，升192點或0.72%；恒生科技指數跑贏大市，暫升1.23%，報5942點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)再度當上升市火車頭，暫升約4%；同系阿里健康(00241)升逾10%，居藍籌升幅榜首。</p>\n</div>",
